Create Classroom
POST /api/classrooms
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "ClassroomName": "Phi"
}

Get All Classrooms
GET /api/classrooms

Get Classroom by ID
GET /api/classrooms/12

Update Classroom
PUT /api/classrooms/12
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "ClassroomName": "Iota"
}

Delete Classroom
DELETE /api/classrooms/12